Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DECIDING ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fought Hym, even I might lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being modest, Larhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In a one-to-one, you would probably win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But in battle, there's compatibility\Nand strengths and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You use your super speed and skills\Nto defeat enemies with blasts and shocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't fight with Aura skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym is still inexperienced in skill,\Nbut has that overwhelming Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's Aura of Light, something\Nthat hurts Mystban the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, a natural enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little bad\Nbeating you up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army was full of\Nannoying characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were the only one\Nwho seemed to respect Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling my, your Aura and life\Nare a dying gift from him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I've got\Na more logical explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want it to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying Hadorra's will gave Hym life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so, too, Little Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles aren't for the evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the 12th member\Nof the righteous Beast King Commandos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere puppet pretending to be\Nthe rebirth of Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget your place, you worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Mystban, shall use all of my power\Nto shatter you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To shatter my Orichalcum body\Nis something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,only one person in the world can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Little Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! At this rate...!{\i0}\N{\i1}This pawn is stronger than I thought!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sadly, I have no choice!{\i0}\N{\i1}I have to use that power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban! Can you not hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He may be fighting Dai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't believe King Ban would be{\i0}\N{\i1}so focused as to not hear my voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! Is it possible that Dai{\i0}\N{\i1}is pressing King Ban that much?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong, Dai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you hesitating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he... Is Ban, the Dark King{\i0}\N{\i1}really this weak?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or is the Minakator spell affecting him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. It barely had any affect on Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be affecting Ban this much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then... I've gotten that much stronger?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To overwhelm an enemy\Nwho once defeated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You question whether it's really me,\Nand can't get a grasp on your own growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,very soon you'll feel euphoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel... euphoric?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To drown in your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a feeling better than\Ndrinking any exquisite wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that a child would understand\Nthe joys of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban is moving to the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Without permission to use that power\NI must fight with what strength I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pour all my Dark Aura\Ninto this hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Aura Ultimate Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's his last ace in the hole\Nfocusing all his Dark Aura into his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, don't let that touch you!\NYou have to dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't dodge this!\NI'll pulverize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot! He's not dodging!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy, Little Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Orichalcum can withstand\Nthe force of my palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now shatter into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you only one person\Ncan shatter this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The best you can do\Nis shatter one arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which lets me get close to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My ace in the hole is my left strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aura Knuckle!{i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Impossible!{\i0}\N{\i1}A mere pawn would defeat me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes!\N-Good going, Little Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking damage\Nto inflict greater damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, my arm can be healed\Nwith a Hoimi-type spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not necessary.\NHe's already unable to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, get his mask off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-King Ban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no. Dai is losing the initiative.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Ban's strange confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that he's really fighting{\i0}\N{\i1}at full strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't be holding back at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why is he so confident?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to win\Nsimply through inertia! Stay aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, don't show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I shall uncloak it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic veil that hides your power...\Nwhile I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That flaming bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've seen it before!{\i0}\N{\i1}I can banish it with an Aban Strash!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A simultaneous attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like they collided at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The mighty Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with my greatest attack,\NI couldn't defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}KAISER PHOENIX{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying to pull his mask off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His identity has long been\Nshrouded in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that his identity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is directly linked\Nto Dark King Ban's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to never speak at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the face he hides,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or his voice, depending on who hears it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great secret that Ban\Ndoesn't want revealed to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in the Dark Army,\NBan to a favoring to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the Six Legion Commanders,\NI probably interacted with Ban the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mystban was my teacher of Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can see his real face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to get a glimpse of the\Nsecret Mystban's been hiding for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can relay that to Dai\Nas he's fighting Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! It could give him an advantage\Nin their final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, this guy won't\Nput up a fight..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finish him whenever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulling off this raiment is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Raiment"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Big Guy?\NWhy are you yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that unveiling Mystban's mask\Ncould be very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't remove Mystban's Shadow Raiment."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before we came here\Nfrom the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku gave me this message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shadow Raiment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the clothes that Mystban wears?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too sure about it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only express it in vague terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no doubt that something\Nis suppressing his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one reason that he and I\Nfought evenly matched for that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I was, he, too,\Nwasn't at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a fight between\Ntwo people holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in that ferocious battle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,During our fight I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,even if he wanted to fight\Nat full strength, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably for a different reason than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What he said when he left was proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maybe if you had fought at full strength
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,our battle wouldn't have taken so long."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Of course, the same could be said of me."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Ron Berku, you're saying\NMystban is still hiding his true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Something's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything that would force him\Nto fight a full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't remove his Shadow Raiment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other word, Ron Berku described
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it is that holds\NMystban's unfathomable power back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as his "Shadow Raiment."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's his mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hym's use of the word raiment\Nmade me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Ron Berku meant\Nif there's a chance to defeat him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,do it before he reveals his true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a good point, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban definitely is unfathomable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ron Berku is the Legendary Craftsman\Nof the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't he be far closer to the secret\Nof the Dark King and Mystban than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't ignore a warning from Ron Berku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! So what do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind either finishing him\Nor revealing his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The final battle with Ban\Nhas already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, it's better that\Nwe finish him off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about his true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We should listen to any warning\Nfrom Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus we need to hurry ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we should get rid of\Nany Dark Army forces that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. That's the right choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if this next blow obliterates\NMystban along with his secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The desire to know it may stem from\Nmy personal feelings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because he was my teacher,\Ndespite it being for evil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, victory comes first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye Mystban!\NHope you rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban! King Ban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was definitely{\i0}\N{\i1}Ban's deciding attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Dai managed to survive it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I could see was{\i0}\N{\i1}up to the instant they clashed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To dive into my Kaiser Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Block my Kaiser Phoenix{\i0}\N{\i1}and my Kōmanotsue hits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Block my staff and the flames consume you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knowing that either way results in damage,{\i0}\N{\i1}you chose to dive into the flames.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A seemingly reckless move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But inside the Phoenix is the only place\Nfrom where one can successfully hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd be hurt either way,\Nso I chose the way where I could hit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course he isn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dark King's strongest spell hit him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A natural result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have managed to strike me,\Nbut my Kaiser Phoenix hit you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were unhurt\Nit would scar my dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for another attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that wound\Nto your shoulder regenerates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my deciding attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, Ban, it's your turn\Nto defend yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I've thought this out right,\NI know I can defeat you with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!\NThen let's see this attack of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doru Aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool. Have you forgotten that\NDoru Aura has no effect on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Doru Aura will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fought Dad once, so I know it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doru Aura is a spell no defense can stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Once cast, there's only\Ntwo ways to survive it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Withstand it or dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you first appeared,\Nnot even your clothes were damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King or not, if you withstood it,\Nyou wouldn't be completely unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you dodged it with a Rura spell,\Nyou wouldn't appear from under the rubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret to how you\Nsurvived my Doru Aura spell must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Kōmanotsue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad hypothesis.\NBut what if you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doru Aura is a spell that drains\Nmassive amounts of Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you can use it more than twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You used it once, so what if I counter\Nafter you've spent all your Magic Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I use this,\Nmy Magic Power will be all spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know you won't counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Doru Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped the Doru Aura with his staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The blade of my Kōmanotsue,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,can be burst forth as an energy wall\Nthat can block any spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you hypothesized,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I survived your Doru Aura by using\Nmy Kōmanotsue to block it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can withstand this, I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver Feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And another!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban vanishes in the light{\i0}\N{\i1}of Dai's second Doru Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shock reaches the White Garden where{\i0}\N{\i1}the others hope to regroup with Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, though Mystban fell before them,{\i0}\N{\i1}he rises once again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and reaches for the raiment{\i0}\N{\i1}that covers him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Shadow Raiment"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
